Core:PCProperties.Core:Property: (\{ (\{ 6, 2 \}), (\{ "h1", "Docktown Clothiers Emporium" \}), (\{ "paragraph", "The Clothiers Emporium is one of the oldest Clothiers Guilds in Docktown, begun within the first year of the opening of the gates to the great city, following in the tradition of of former Artisans Guild Leader Jade, we at the Emporium strive to maintain low prices for our new denizens as well as catering to some of our older, wealthier visitors.\\r\\n\\r\\n" \}), (\{ "paragraph", "The Emporium suffered a great loss with Mistress Tessa's lengthy disappearance but has renewed itself again, Under the Charge of Mave, her steadfast apprentice.\\r\\n\\r\\nNow with Both back we hope to fill our ranks once again, and continue the service we so long ago provided.\\r\\n\\r\\nMay you all be well,\\r\\n \\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n " \}), (\{ "h3", " Mistress Contessa ThellorKilanth Agria Noami L'sqain\\r\\n Apprentice Mave\\r\\n" \}) \})
